### Get account balance
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exchange/account/balance?exchangeType=binance

### Get total asset value
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exchange/account/total-value?exchangeType=binance

### Get position profit for a specific symbol
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exchange/profit/BTC-USDT?exchangeType=binance

### Get position profit for a specific symbol with position side
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exchange/profit/BTC-USDT?exchangeType=binance&positionSide=long

### Get all profits
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exchange/profit?exchangeType=binance

